{"tid":1941833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣324事件6周年","createTime":"2020-03-24T16:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T17:05:16.000Z","uid":25259,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b0a0d23f75c3b5a3f370b0c7e2b6178a44d2fe16","tid":1941833,"uid":25259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T16:08:43.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩睇完最新一集眼球中央電視台, <br />\n片既最後主播視網膜提到324六周年、拍肩警等等既keyword<br />\n就上網查下咩事, 原來係六年前台灣反黑箱服貿時<br />\n學生市民佔領立法院而被警察暴力清場 (時任總統馬英九)<br />\n而當時行政院長江宜樺事後稱警員只係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>「拍肩」、「抬離」</strong></span></span>驅趕市民<br />\n直到而加都仲未搵哂當年既警暴人員出黎控告<br />\n<br />\n而八掛google search既時候就發現黎個清晰時序既網站，作為網頁文宣黎講好高質<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HfpVnBp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfpVnBp.png&h=d38e48c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WYDK0n3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWYDK0n3.png&h=d5e67eb6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcyi4PJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmcyi4PJ.png&h=99505bed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n詳細可以禁入去:<br />\n<a href=\"https://324.jrf.org.tw/?fbclid=IwAR1gxRMfWldFTmaKIFg8l76IQ6Bcam8pztwd3ozhdJjhQrXG8zCmdH3AEyI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F324.jrf.org.tw%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1gxRMfWldFTmaKIFg8l76IQ6Bcam8pztwd3ozhdJjhQrXG8zCmdH3AEyI&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=506a4011\" target=\"_blank\">https://324.jrf.org.tw/?fbclid=IwAR1gxRMfWldFTmaKIFg8l76IQ6Bcam8pztwd3ozhdJjhQrXG8zCmdH3AEyI</a><br />\n<br />\n無獨有偶, 佔中時既警暴事件「七警毆打案」係2017年既判決亦加深左台灣人對於成功追究警暴既信心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>尋找拍肩警：香港佔中「七警毆打案」判決對臺灣的啟示</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://opinion.udn.com/opinion/story/10847/2292248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopinion.udn.com%2Fopinion%2Fstory%2F10847%2F2292248&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=0d98871e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://opinion.udn.com/opinion/story/10847/2292248</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣人係反送中時對香港人既支持, 大家都應該感受到<br />\n希望大家都可以係唔同渠道表達返對台灣人追究警暴既支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【表情凶狠、高舉警棍，行政院前「系統無法比對」的警察】#324六週年</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/search/top/?q=324%20%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B&amp;epa=SEARCH_BOX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsearch%2Ftop%2F%3Fq%3D324%2520%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%26epa%3DSEARCH_BOX&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=0805a03e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/search/top/?q=324%20%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B&amp;epa=SEARCH_BOX</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【歷史上的今天】3月24日──324行政院驅離事件</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ftvnews53/photos/pb.235679595900.-2207520000../10157795053105901/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fftvnews53%2Fphotos%2Fpb.235679595900.-2207520000..%2F10157795053105901%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=bb825f58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ftvnews53/photos/pb.235679595900.-2207520000../10157795053105901/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"f7b69dced4b594aa6a24d18e93ed7c1f32f57ff4","tid":1941833,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e3e8740cd72209683b648c757beb797c6b03e5fa","tid":1941833,"uid":148204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T16:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb71c13d615c9f2cbcdc744d9747804859270f52","tid":1941833,"uid":49353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"038310cf07f46256de07e5b8b37ec9f007d304a4","tid":1941833,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2